# Admin Guide
## Vaccinations
The 'Vaccinations' toolis designed to help the parents monitor the vaccinations induced on their child or children. It envolepes the due dates on when to dose their chil or children and the missed appointments. Furthermore, each supplements have an information of their purose and what diseases it prevents. 
### Components
1. Vaccinatination Summary
2. Milestone
### Vaccination Summary
It entails the administered vaccine, to be administered vaccines, and missed vaccines
### Milestones
It states the month of parents' child or children with the expected vaccine, next vaccine schedule, and which to be administered
### Navigating Milestones
The milestones are right under the 'Vaccination Summary'
1. Click either the 'Upcomming' button or 'Previous' button to see the current administered vaccines.
2. Click down the rectangular box with drop-down arrow to see further details about the induced or to be induced vaccine
3. Tap the 'Read more about this vaccine' to see deeper insights about the vaccines
4. Click the 'share' button on the left side of the screen to share on social media platforms about the vaccine, if desired.
5. Click the 'save' button on the right side of the screen to store the information on 'Favorites' tab, if desired
6. Click the related advice to read more about the vaccines and other related topics about it, if desired
7. Tap on the left arrow to go back to the Vaccines page once done reading about the desired information
8. Tap on the coloured button to read about the latter
9. Repeat the 3rd step until 7th step if you wish to learn more about the vaccines and to share it with your friends. 